data.description: Welcome to this well-kept 4 Bedroom and 2.5 bath home in the heart of Pittsburg.  Old town Pittsburg just minutes away with lots of shopping and restaurants, with close proximity to freeways.  Bright and welcoming floorplan boasts large living room and spacious kitchen with lots of cabinetry.  The 4 large bedrooms are nicely appointed upstairs with a large primary bedroom with on suite bathroom.  Brand new AC was just put in last year as well and new vinyl flooring throughout.  Don't miss this opportunity to live comfortably tucked away in a secure gated community in Pittsburg!
